Package: scCDC
Type: Package
Title: Single-cell (-nucleus) RNA Sequencing Data Contamination
        Detection and Correction
Version: 1.3
Date: 2023-12-12
Author: Weijian Wang, Yihui Cen, Zezhen Lu
Maintainer: Yihui Cen <yihuicen@g.ucla.edu>
Description: This package uses entropy theory to detect contaminated genes and perform 
             decontamination process using Youden index-based Method. It offers a fast 
             procedure to allow users to targets contaminations and remove them.
